<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.2">
<l>palla vantikaḻ pūṅkaṭam pēṟiyak kāḷiyaṉ paṇavaraṅkil</l>
<l>ollai vantuṟap pāyntaru naṭañceyta</l>
<l>vumparkō ṉuṟaikōyil</l>
<l>nalla ventaḻal mūṉṟunāl vētamai vēḷviyō ṭāṟaṅkam</l>
<l>valla vantaṇar malkiya nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells the celestials’ king who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having climbed a flowering katamba with [new] shoots glistening,</l>
<l>And arriving suddenly, leaping to reach the stage</l>
<l rend="indent">which was that Kāliya’s hood, performed a rare dance on [it],</l>
<l>Is Vaṉpuruṭōttamam in Nānkūr where flourish priests</l>
<l rend="indent">skilled in the auspicious three blazing fires,</l>
<l>The four Vedas, the five sacrifices, [and] the six branches [of knowledge].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
